					<p><span class="emphasis">Helping Others to Help Themselves: The Story of the Mormon Church Welfare Program</span> (1945), 4.</p>
				</li>
				<li class="footnote " id="-10411_000_021"><a name="-10411_000_021">&nbsp;</a>
					<span class="label"><a name="footnote8-10411_000_021">8.</a></span>
					<p>Richard&nbsp;C. Edgley, &ldquo;This Is Your Phone Call,&rdquo; <span class="emphasis">Liahona</span> and <span class="emphasis">Ensign,</span> May 2009, 54.</p>
				</li>
